divs: Sighting DetailsThe day before Thanksgiving 1991 on SH 70 about 2 miles NW of Frederick, MD We were driving to Penn for Thanksgiving. I seen something 100 feet above the high wires it wasn't moving it was suspended in midair there was no sound . There were strobe like lights at first I thought it was a CH-47 Chinook but it had no rotors. The highway is split on ether side cars were stopped there were 6 or 7 MD. state troopers telling people they can't stop on the side of the road a lot of people stayed we went !
